        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，三个节点横向排列。我想确认一下：LMS门户和StudentDB之间是双向数据交换还是单向的？成绩同步是独立系统还是依赖前两者？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "都是单向的。LMS门户把登录和课程数据推给StudentDB，然后GradeSync从StudentDB拉取学生信息来完成成绩同步。没有反向回流。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画一版：LMS门户在最左，箭头指向中间的StudentDB，再一个箭头指向最右的GradeSync。三个节点水平排列，方向LR。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "节点命名上，我想用更简洁的标识。LMS门户叫A，StudentDB叫B，GradeSync叫C，这样讨论起来方便。显示文本保持完整名称。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "B",
        "C",
        "Education_LMS_Portal",
        "Education_StudentDB",
        "Education_GradeSync"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
